    "Additionally, algorithms dedicated to deblurring counteract motion or optical-induced blurriness, restoring sharpness.",
    "Denoising techniques (Tian et al. 2018; Peng et al. March 2020; Tian and Fei 2020) such as Total Variation Denoising (TVD) and Non-Local Means (NLM) further contribute by effectively reducing random noise while preserving essential image details, collectively advancing the field's capacity to improve image integrity and visual clarity.",
